/2026/1/5295952b-b51f-467a-aca6-00affd17518e.png\"/>\n<br>b. Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/e8d4dcba-af5a-46a7-9a1f-999aafd21ac3.png\"/> có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/7010414a-e295-4706-8b4f-881e1506582b.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/6f7c082a-cb92-48c3-902a-81e35fca3d1d.png\"/> (Định lý Thales đảo)\n<br>3) Ta có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/91cd3483-1a62-416b-8e63-9e3be1805053.png\"/> nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/d2e31b2f-1274-4ed8-97e5-81ce2e2c6b28.png\"/>\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/d00eed47-a475-4cf0-9276-f5a0083f9d65.png\"/> suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/d10d102c-057f-44fb-adb8-88ff34354f12.png\"/> (Hệ quả thales)\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/96132481-24dc-467f-9207-dc405dc1b198.png\"/> suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/0d753e9c-d1cc-4c49-a9d3-d6399c937c74.png\"/> (Hệ quả thales)\n<br>Từ đó, suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/6d46a18f-90f4-4ba6-ae77-aa9c8be99ead.png\"/> mà <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/efc82a47-e8a6-44cb-9963-fb6c520e8747.png\"/> (gt) nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/c675ac9f-ca76-4a09-8ddd-b4bc95fe4687.png\"/> hay I là trung điểm <i>MN</i> suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/420d1193-fa76-4945-ad56-5859bf0c3c84.png\"/>\n",
